<%-include('./template/top',{});%>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%-include('./template/navbar', { config:{ transparent:true, colorScroll: 400 } });%>
    <!-- End Navbar -->
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="page-header clear-filter" filter-color="orange">
            <div class="page-header-image" data-parallax="true" style="background-image: url('/img/livros.jpg');">
            </div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-md-4 content-center search-content">

                    <div class="brand search-header">
                        <img class="n-logo" src="/img/logo-I-001.png" alt="">
                        <form class="form" method="GET" action="/publicacoes">
                            <div class="content">
                                <div class="input-group form-group-no-border input-lg search-div">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control search-input" placeholder="Palavra-chave" name="filtro">
                                    <button class="btn search-advanced" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#pesquisaAvancada">Avançada</button>
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn search-span">
                                        <span>
                                            <i class="now-ui-icons ui-1_zoom-bold"></i>
                                        </span>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="section section-tabs">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3 class="title">Últimas públicações</h3>
                    <div class="row">
                        <%for(var i = 0; i<publicacoes.length; i++){%>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                        <%- include('./publicacao/card', { publicacao: publicacoes[i] } );%>
                        </div>
                        <%- include('./publicacao/modal', { publicacao: publicacoes[i] } );%>
                        <%}%>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Sart Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="pesquisaAvancada" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="pesquisaAvancada" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header justify-content-center">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">
                            <i class="now-ui-icons ui-1_simple-remove"></i>
                        </button>
                        <h4 class="title title-up">Modal title</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <p>Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts. Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default">Nice Button</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--  End Modal -->
        
        <footer class="footer" data-background-color="black">
            <div class="container">
                
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
<%-include('./template/bottom',{});%>